<blockquote>"Here comes the story of the Hurricane
The man the authorities came to blame"
~ Bob Dylan</blockquote>While this is not the same story that Dylan sang about, Michael Lewis offers unique insights into the hurricane life of Sam Bankman-Fried, Boy Billionaire, Convicted Criminal.

Five Business Lessons Learned:

~ When you have no skill in management—and have no interest in learning—hire someone who is both experienced and capable.

~ When you start up two companies, don't commingle funds between them.

~ When your companies feature millions of dollars of transactions, hire a CFO to manage the process.

~ Don't pay Tom Brady $55 million for approximately 60 hours of promotional work, EVER!

~ When your lawyers tell you to keep your mouth shut, keep your mouth shut.
